comment: Crabbe (POR) jumps and lands prior to releasing the ball.
Batum (POR) cleanly knocks the ball away from Thompson (GSW) after the rebound is secured.
Bogut (GSW) sets the screen on Lillard (POR) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Lillard (POR) takes three steps after he ends his dribble on the drive to the basket.
There is incidental contact between Curry (GSW) and McCollum (POR) on the perimeter.
